<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="id4742bd2e-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1998—<ref href="/us/pl/105/206">Pub. L. 105–206</ref> renumbered <ref href="/us/usc/t26/s7123">section 7123 of this title</ref> as this section.</p>
