<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Subsec. (b). <ref href="/us/pl/97/258/s3/f/12/B">Pub. L. 97–258, § 3(f)(12)(B)</ref>, struck out subsec. (b) which set forth cross reference to R.S. 3469 (<ref href="/us/usc/t31/s194">31 U.S.C. 194</ref>) relating to compromises after judgment.</p>
